title: Tony Khan Says Collision Was Last AEW Event In Venue Until After Renovations
summary: Tomorrow's "AEW Collision" will reportedly be the last episode filmed in the promotion's home venue before major renovations take place.

title: Backstage Report On Kota Ibushi's AEW Collision Injury
summary: Kota Ibushi suffered a serious injury during a recent "AEW Collision" taping, and there has been an update on what type of injury he sustained.
